### Inventory Management System API Test

### 1. Create a new product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop",
  "description": "High-performance gaming laptop with RTX 4080",
  "stockQuantity": 50,
  "lowStockThreshold": 5
}

### 2. Get all products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### 3. Get product by ID (replace {id} with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### 4. Update product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop Pro",
  "description": "Updated high-performance gaming laptop with RTX 4080",
  "stockQuantity": 45,
  "lowStockThreshold": 8
}

### 5. Increase stock
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/1/stock/increase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 20
}

### 6. Decrease stock
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/1/stock/decrease
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 15
}

### 7. Try to decrease stock beyond available (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/1/stock/decrease
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 100
}

### 8. Create a low stock product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Mouse",
  "description": "Ergonomic wireless mouse",
  "stockQuantity": 3,
  "lowStockThreshold": 10
}

### 9. Get low stock products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/low-stock

### 10. Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### 11. Try to get deleted product (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### 12. Test validation - invalid product (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "Invalid product",
  "stockQuantity": -5,
  "lowStockThreshold": -1
}

### 13. Test validation - invalid stock update (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/2/stock/increase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 0
}